name: Scanning The Horizon
description:
Animated gif loop by Jean Poole, 1000 x 1000 pixels, 34 frames.

An experiment in disintegration and collage... 
 
... and a dip of the toes in 2021, before exploring a range of animations and filmed projections in 2022.

https://skynoise.net
https://twitter.com/jean_poole_art
